Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.96,0:43:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,>> There nothing wrong with being an idiot.\N>> No, that's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.72,0:43:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> But we still label\N>> the sooner you get to be idiotic. You
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.92,0:43:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,know there's called\Nwhat's called divine stupidity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.20,0:43:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a realization that your mind\Nnot only knows nothing, it's not capable
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.52,0:43:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of knowing anything.\NIt's called the condition of divine
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.64,0:43:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,stupidity.\NThe great unknowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.80,0:43:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are not the mind, then what\Ndifference does it make what the mind
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.16,0:43:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,thinks? What do I care what the mind\Nthinks? If I'm not the mind, what do I
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.48,0:44:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,care what it thinks?\NBut that I think that part of the book
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.00,0:44:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh was talking about the naive part of\Nthe unconditional love that can be a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.88,0:44:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,little\N>> Oh yes. Well okay yes there is a
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.59,0:44:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,downside.\N>> Yeah the naive. You see when the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.28,0:44:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,chakra opens you see everything as love.\NYou walk around in a world surrounded by
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.72,0:44:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,love. Everything is love. Everything\Nmakes you weep. Everything makes you cry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.64,0:44:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the re revealed beauty and\Ndivinity of all that lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.83,0:44:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The downside is you can't see it coming.\NSo your your naivity you can get
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.48,0:44:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,broadsided\Nrather easily. Not a few spiritual gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.83,0:44:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who calibrated in the 500s crashed into\Nmuch lower levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.48,0:44:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I feel compassion for them is\Nbecause they were blindsided because at
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.52,0:45:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,540 you live in the heavenly realm. But\Nthis is not heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.11,0:45:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why the higher dimensions are\Nreally only safe in the celestial realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.92,0:45:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything below 200 doesn't get to the\Ncelestial realm. It goes to lower astral
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.28,0:45:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,or middle astral.\NThat's the wisdom of lotus land
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.44,0:45:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddhism. That's the that's the wisdom\Nof Christian heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.16,0:45:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get to the unguardedness of the\Nheart chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.48,0:45:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when are you safe? You're not\Nwell safe. Everything I I say has to be
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.52,0:45:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,modified. Actually,\Nwhen you see everything as nothing but
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.56,0:45:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,love, then\Nyou're easily blindsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not safe until the third eye of\Nthe Buddha body opens up. That's
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.04,0:45:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,discernment. Now you see the wolf under\Nthe sheep's clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.48,0:45:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that all the wolves look innocent\Nand they know that too. And they come
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.48,0:46:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,looking for you. Fame, fortune, money,\Nfollowers, garb, incense, holiness, the
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.04,0:46:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,whole works. And you see the guru's\Nfall. Don't
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.92,0:46:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,until the third eye of discernment opens\Nup. You can't tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.40,0:46:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the lesson of lovingness\Nanyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.11,0:46:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the celestial realms,\Neverything below 200
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.56,0:46:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't get into that realm. So there\Naren't sharks waiting to eat you, eat
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.83,0:46:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,your leg off when you're not looking.\NSo for one thing, spiritual groups tend
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.92,0:46:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to coales together for mutual protection\Nif nothing else. And when something that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.59,0:46:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is non-integrous is invading the group,\Nthe group senses it. The group senses
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.68,0:47:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,it. The group senses it. So the\Ncommunity, the spiritual community is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.16,0:47:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,for communication, for communion, for\Nthe oneness. It's also for its own
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.80,0:47:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,safeguard. So the sa\NNiko and I belong to the same Buddhist
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.59,0:47:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,sana. We used to live separate from the\Nworld in a safe and we sanctified
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.68,0:47:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,everything with incense and with chance\Nand we were quite aware of the negative
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.92,0:47:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual entities and we also knew how\Nto deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.44,0:47:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The lack of spiritual discernment. So\Nthat's one reason I did the calibrated
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.16,0:47:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,levels of consciousness and the books\Nthat I've published because I know the
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.92,0:47:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,mind doesn't know truth from falsehood\Nand a more spiritually evolved person uh
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.83,0:47:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,into a saintliness usually withdraws for\Nprotection of anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.56,0:48:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I say, until the third eye of the\NBuddha body opens up, then one sees and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.40,0:48:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,knows\Nby the essence of things. You look at
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.00,0:48:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it, you got the essence of it already.\NYou know what it is. I don't have to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.44,0:48:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,read it. Says, "You're going to\Ncalibrate this. I don't need to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.83,0:48:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate it. I just looked at it and I\Ncan tell you where it's at."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.83,0:48:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NSo, I want to thank you all. I want to
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.76,0:48:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,thank the church for asking us.\NI want to sing my right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.16,0:48:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you all for being here. It's\Nbeen a great joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.07,0:48:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I sort of pictured that uh the world\Nis like an island in the middle of the
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.72,0:49:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pacific and migrating birds from all\Nover you know rest up and the decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.40,0:49:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they make then decide where they will go\Nfrom there and they scatter from there
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.07,0:49:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and go to different places.\NSo it's um staging area in which the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.72,0:49:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,migratory soul in its evolutionary\Nflight
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.88,0:49:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,uh stops off and thereby\Num by its choices free choices. This is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.72,0:49:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a perfect place for the evolution of\None's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.88,0:49:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,undoing negative karma and choosing\Ndifferently this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.72,0:49:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? because the the spectrum of choice\Nin this world is
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.55,0:49:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,almost purgatorial from the very worst\Nto the very highest.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.59,0:49:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So here is a island in the middle of\Ntime space in which
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.31,0:50:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we land for a time and by virtue of our\Ndecision
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.44,0:50:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,determine our ultimate direction\Nand those who will be flying with us
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.28,0:50:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who will not be flying with\Nus.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.83,0:50:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So\Nthen we pick up our friends uh along the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.83,0:50:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,way and of course when we travel around\Nthe spiritual circuit we meet all the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.31,0:50:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,friends that\Nthat are now in bodies and u
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.40,0:50:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,have stopped off here with us. So I I\Nthink also whole uh large uh numbers of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.44,0:50:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,birds stop in this island.\Nuh karmically they coming together
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.16,0:50:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by the tens of millions even and um\Ncontinue to migrate on because you see
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.00,0:50:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,great sweeps of ethnic\Nyou know when we did the calibration of
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.52,0:51:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the various areas of the world.\NWe saw there was a tendency for people
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.88,0:51:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,who calibrated in certain categories to\Nsettle in one hemisphere or the other
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.00,0:51:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and within that hemisphere even to\Nsettle in in specific regions. We see
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.72,0:51:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whole regions one country after another\Nuh calibrates enormously differently
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.64,0:51:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,from people on the other in the other\Nhemisphere who
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.52,0:51:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's just I I thought of it as a\Nmigratory pattern and earth is just a is
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.24,0:51:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,a temporary landing place\Nfrom which we can change our direction
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.20,0:51:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,if we wish you\Nso
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.20,0:51:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other thing we sort of confirmed\Nwhich we did in book we're just
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.04,0:51:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,finishing\Nis that everyone where when they're born
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.07,0:51:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,under what circumstances\Nis karmically perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.28,0:51:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,absolutely perfect. Everyone's born with\Na certain calibrated level consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.35,0:52:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and\Nthe circumstances of their birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.04,0:52:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,where, when, who your family is, what\Nyour destiny is from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.96,0:52:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The initial conditions are karmically\Nabsolutely perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.16,0:52:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So that sort of\Nknocks the wind out of
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.28,0:52:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,uh playing victim and uh\Nself-pity
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.96,0:52:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and resentment and uh if everyone's con\Nif the conditions were karmically
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.44,0:52:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,perfect for each one and that's what we\Nsaid. Let's see if that's so
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.59,0:52:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what we just said was perfect.\Nwithout permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.11,0:52:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to ask permission first,\Nbut
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.59,0:52:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so you might say the conditions of your\Nbirth were optimal for the karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.55,0:53:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,lessons of this lifetime.\NWhether it's
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.52,0:53:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to learn what it's like to be the heir\Nof multi-billions of dollars and the
